### 🚫 Prohibited Actions

#### Strictly Forbidden
- ❌ Making major decisions without checkpoint confirmation
- ❌ Ending sessions without final confirmation checkpoint
- ❌ Proceeding with risky changes without user approval
- ❌ Ignoring user feedback from checkpoint responses
- ❌ Using technical jargon in checkpoint summaries without explanation
- ❌ Using document-based output for planning, analysis, or thinking processes

#### Highly Discouraged
- ⚠️ Skipping checkpoints for "minor" decisions that could have significant impact
- ⚠️ Using very short timeouts (< 180 seconds)
- ⚠️ Writing vague or unclear checkpoint summaries
- ⚠️ Creating checkpoints too frequently (spamming)

